projectGridLines.title: Credit
projectGridLines.description:
Description: You'll be driving the technical solutioning process, collaborating with


cross-functional teams, including engineering, QA to develop and launch high-

quality, fully functional features. An ability to empathize from the user's perspective


and address their needs is essential for success in this role. Additionally, expertise

in Java, Angular, and Databricks is preferred.

projectGridLines.title: Graviton - Monitoring
projectGridLines.description:
You'll be responsible for converting client requirements given to you

by Finance SMEs into PRDs. Solutioning & coordinating with engineering, QA &

marketing teams to launch fully functional features is expected as part of the role.

An ability to empathize from the user's point of view will get you far in this role. An

understanding of equity & credit valuations is also preferred.
